Prepare pudding as directed on package except use 2 cups of milk and almond extract. Fold in 1 cup of the whipped topping. Layer 1/3 of cake, 1/3 of fruit, 1/3 of pudding mixture in 3-quart trifle or glass bowl. Repeat with 2 more layers using all cake, fruit and pudding. Spread with remaining whipped topping. Cover and refrigerate at least 2 hours or overnight.